        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="flows" value="1. User signs in via Google&#xa;2. App authenticates with Firebase Auth&#xa;3a. User adds/edits receipt or warranty&#xa;3b. User views/ filters items list&#xa;4. User requests to delete item&#xa;5a. Save item to local Room DB&#xa;5b. Query items from Room DB&#xa;6. Delete from Room DB&#xa;7a. Upload image to Google Drive&#xa;7b. Upload item data to Firestore&#xa;8a. Delete from Firestore&#xa;8b. Delete image from Drive&#xa;9a. Full sync with Firestore&#xa;9b. Merge cloud/local data (timestamp-based)&#xa;9c. Upload/download images to Drive&#xa;10. Schedule WorkManager reminder&#xa;11. Notification triggered to user&#xa;12. Export data to CSV file" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#666666;fillColor=#f5f5f5;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=9" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="550" width="240" height="300" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
